title: Men's Athletic Cushioned Ankle Socks Comfort Wicking Anti-Blister Running Sock 5 Pairs
description: Anti-blister Protection: The heel tab provide extra comfort and protection, easy to put on and take off. The padding across the achilles tendon, prevents blisters on the ankle and heel. Lycra elastic cuff can lock the ankle, prevents slipping off

Soft and Cozy Cushioned Socks: These mens socks with great soft cushioning at the bottom, heel and toe areas provide comfort, anti-blister protection, absorb shock and relieve foot pain when training, walking, running, golf, tennis etc

Wicking Socks for Men: Made of high quality polyester and moisture control fibers for extra softness, comfort and durable while retaining sweat-wicking. Mesh plates help to ventilate release the heat, keep your feet cool and dry

Arch Compression Support: Our mens ankle socks have suitable compression in arch can provide full motion support and stability, relieve foot fatigue and swelling, fit your feet perfectly and keep socks in place

Reinforced Heel & Toe: The toe and heel areas are reinforced for durability in high-wear areas. Elastic spandex and sturdy yarn material to withstand repeated wear. After Multiple washings, the socks still keep their original shape
